Raov()

# 
teaching_method <- factor(rep(c("A", "B", "C"), each = 10))
score <- c(85, 88, 90, 87, 86, 89, 91, 92, 84, 87,
           78, 82, 80, 79, 81, 83, 85, 84, 80, 81,
           92, 94, 93, 95, 91, 90, 96, 94, 93, 92)

# 
data <- data.frame(TeachingMethod = teaching_method, Score = score)
